Her husband, Joseph, was a righteous man. He did not want to shame her publicly. So, he decided to divorce her quietly.
But while he was thinking about this, an angel of the Lord appeared to him in a dream and said, "Joseph, son of David, do not be afraid to take Mary as your wife, for that which is conceived in her is from the Holy Spirit."
She will give birth to a son. Name him Jesus. For he will save his people from their sins.
